      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/gcbp-hemolysis-bench-comparison",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "FDA GCBP bench-top hemolysis comparison — 5 operating points",
      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against in-vitro measurements from the FDA interlaboratory study across 5 flow-speed combinations. Mean relative error 8.3%; all predictions within experimental uncertainty band.",
      "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "https://doi.org/10.1115/1.4034270"
    },
    {
